        in the next 3-5 years?
    </h3>

    <p>Out of the total 1605 respondents, 1145 responded to these questions.</p>

    <ol>
        <li><p>Increased quality employment for individuals with disabilities</p></li>

        <li><p>Marketing, outreach and education</p></li>

        <li><p>Improved DOR personnel and business process</p></li>

        <li><p>Increased advocacy</p></li>

        <li><p>Effective legislation</p></li>

        <li><p>Increased accessibility</p></li>

        <li><p>Increased community based living/housing and independence </p></li>
